payload.text:
The splash screen duration is controlled by a `setTimeout` function inside the **`App.tsx`** file.

Currently, it is set to **3000 milliseconds** (3 seconds).

You can find it in this block of code:

```typescript
  useEffect(() => {
    const timer = setTimeout(() => {
      setShowSplash(false);
    }, 3000); // <--- This number sets the duration (3 seconds)

    return () => clearTimeout(timer);
  }, []);

